PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 44 - which (a) DECLARES the severe flooding which occured in NEW BRUNSWICK on January 21, 2000, to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.

precis:
Enactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 44 -
which (a) DECLARES the severe flooding which occured in NEW BRUNSWICK on
January 21, 2000, to be of concern to the federal government, and
(b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.
